<!-- About Page -->
<section class="page profile-page" id="aboutPage" style="display: block; padding-top: 2rem;">
    <div class="page-container">
        <div class="profile-reservations glass-card">
            <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">About This Project</h2>
            <p>Labubu is a Computer Lab Reservation System developed by group members: Ralph Del Rosario, Zach Hallare, Keifer Sy, and Farrell Tadina.</p>
            <br>
            <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; margin-top: 1rem;">NPM Packages (Backend)</h3>
            <ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 2rem; line-height: 1.6;">
                <li><strong>bcrypt</strong>: For securely hashing and comparing passwords.</li>
                <li><strong>dotenv</strong>: For loading environment variables from a .env file.</li>
                <li><strong>express</strong>: The core web framework for Node.js used for routing and handling HTTP requests.</li>
                <li><strong>express-handlebars</strong>: A Handlebars view engine for rendering HTML templates.</li>
                <li><strong>express-session</strong>: Used to manage user sessions for authentication state.</li>
                <li><strong>mongoose</strong>: An Object Data Modeling (ODM) library for MongoDB and Node.js.</li>
            </ul>
            <br>
            <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; margin-top: 1rem;">Third-Party Libraries (Frontend)</h3>
            <ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 2rem; line-height: 1.6;">
                <li><strong>Google Fonts (Inter)</strong>: For custom typography and clean user interface styling.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

